OL,3,C'A historic day for Mexican cuisine':
OL,4,CMexico City taco stand given Michelin
OL,5,Cstar
OL,7,FA taco stand in Mexico City has been
OL,8,Fgiven a Michelin star - making it one
OL,9,Fof the smallest ever restaurants to
OL,10,Freceive the exclusive honour.
OL,12,FTacos El Califa de Leon has only four
OL,13,Foptions on the menu, all of which are
OL,14,Fvariations of beef tacos. Customers
OL,15,Fcan choose from beef rib, loin, or
OL,16,Ffore shank.
