OL,3,C'A historic day for Mexican cuisine':
OL,4,CMexico City taco stand given Michelin
OL,5,Cstar
OL,7,FThere is no place to sit by the stand,
OL,8,Fmeaning customers stand on the
OL,9,Fpavement to eat. On some days,
OL,10,Fcustomers are forced out onto the
OL,11,Fstreet, the pavement jammed with other
OL,13,FAsked whether they would make room for
OL,14,Fa seating area, the stand's owner,
OL,15,FHernandez Alonso, expressed an "if it
OL,16,Fain't broke, don't fix it" attitude.
OL,18,F"It's the way God ordered things," he
OL,19,Fsaid, "and you have to deal with it."
