OL,3,C'A historic day for Mexican cuisine':
OL,4,CMexico City taco stand given Michelin
OL,5,Cstar
OL,7,Fvisited the stand on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fpresenting the chef, Arturo Rivera
OL,9,FMartinez with one of the company's
OL,10,Fdistinctive white chef's jackets.
OL,12,FBut the stand's newly-minted chef
OL,13,Frefused to wear the jacket - it was
OL,14,Ftoo hot inside the stand's tiny, 3x3
OL,15,Fmetre kitchen.
OL,17,FAsked how it felt to get a Michelin
OL,18,Fstar, Rivera Martinez, who is the
OL,19,Fowner Alonso's son, responded, "esta
OL,20,Fchido, esta padre" - "it's neat, it's
OL,21,Fcool."
