OL,3,C'A historic day for Mexican cuisine':
OL,4,CMexico City taco stand given Michelin
OL,5,Cstar
OL,7,FMartinez's grandfather, Juan, founded
OL,8,Fthe business in 1968 - and they have
OL,9,Fchanged little since.
OL,11,F"The secret is the simplicity of our
OL,12,Ftaco," said Rivera Martinez.
OL,14,F"It has only a tortilla, red or green
OL,15,Fsauce, and that's it. That, and the
OL,16,Fquality of the meat," he added.
