OL,3,C'A historic day for Mexican cuisine':
OL,4,CMexico City taco stand given Michelin
OL,5,Cstar
OL,7,FThe tacos are made with a pinch of
OL,8,Fsalt, a squeeze of lime, and a soft
OL,9,Fround of freshly rolled tortilla
OL,10,Fdough. Any sauces are added by the
OL,11,Fcustomer.
OL,13,FThe prices are relatively high
OL,14,Fbystandards: a single taco costs
OL,15,Fnearly $5 (#4). But many customers are
OL,16,Fconvinced it's the best in the city.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/7
