OL,3,C'A historic day for Mexican cuisine':
OL,4,CMexico City taco stand given Michelin
OL,5,Cstar
OL,7,FOne customer, who had been going to
OL,8,Fthe stand for eight years, said he has
OL,9,F"never been disappointed" by the
OL,10,Ftacos, citing the quality of the meat.
OL,11,F"I'll recommend it with even more
OL,12,Freason now that it has a star," he
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FHe was queueing for a taco alongside
OL,16,Fhis son, who noted, "this is a
OL,17,Fhistoric day for Mexican cuisine, and
OL,18,Fwe're witnesses to it."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/7
