OL,8,Fstreet vendors that have won a
OL,9,FMichelin star, including a Chinese
OL,10,Ffood kiosk in Singapore and a Thai
OL,11,Fstreet food stand in Bangkok. But
OL,12,FTacos El Califa de Leon is Mexico's
OL,13,Ffirst.
